{
  "name": "Expert Barbarian",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/creatures/abilities/bull-head-horns-glowing.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You gain the following benefits for your Barbarian Class Features.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Rage</span></strong></span></p><p>You can immediately enter a <strong>Rage</strong> for free as a Reaction upon rolling for Initiative.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Berserker</span></strong></span></p><p>Charge now grants 3 Spaces of movement. The movement granted by your <strong>Charge</strong> ignores Difficult Terrain.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Battlecry</span></strong></p><p>The range of Battlecry increases to 10 Spaces.</p><p>When you use Battlecry you can spend additional SP to enhance the effect:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Enhanced Fortitude Shout:</strong> (1 SP) They gain Resistance (Half) instead.</p></li><li><p><strong>Enhanced Fury Shout:</strong> (3 SP) The additional damage increases by 1.</p></li><li><p><strong>Enhanced Urgent Shout:</strong> (Up to 2 SP) The speed gained is increased by 2 per SP spent.</p></li></ul>",
